{"tid":1154293,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"小紅書可以用黎趕走大陸人","createTime":"2019-05-14T07:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T09:23:10.000Z","uid":199982,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d7a34595b0f0094d0726bada8a4409cee3c08a0d","tid":1154293,"uid":199982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T07:50:34.000Z","msg":"無論係零三年沙士 定係今年嘅豬瘟<br />\n都係大陸傳入黎香港<br />\n但係你又吹個垃圾政府唔脹 <br />\n永遠唔阻止蝗蟲入境 又等到事態嚴重先公布疫情<br />\n咁可以點做？<br />\n咪用返佢哋最鍾意嘅小紅書黎散播消息囉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FjVcAto.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFjVcAto.png&h=6a78ff7c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zPpXMz4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzPpXMz4.png&h=f088c720&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n入面全部都係事實 唔係製造恐慌㗎<br />\n<br />\n樓下Comment個位小姐 <br />\n我係想曲線令到班大陸人唔敢黎姐 請多多見諒 <br />\n不過佢一直接指出大陸做嘅衰野 啲人就走黎撩交嗌<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家俾啲ideas 令到啲蝗唔再黎香港<br />\n冇人需要佢地黎搞到香港烏煙瘴氣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KmGnXKi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKmGnXKi.jpg&h=6d19c153&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"026ccdf38ebaa27897cadd13729db64ebcdb2cde","tid":1154293,"uid":199982,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T08:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Vxyj3x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Vxyj3x.png&h=a7dc0744&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n屌你老母 違反咗啲咩規例？<br />\n言論自由都冇仲想學人做強國<br />\n不如索性資訊封鎖 令全國變文盲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9297535ecb2c9ef29b88dceade564b87a6393232","tid":1154293,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7a34595b0f0094d0726bada8a4409cee3c08a0d","tid":1154293,"uid":199982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T07:50:34.000Z","msg":"無論係零三年沙士 定係今年嘅豬瘟<br />\n都係大陸傳入黎香港<br />\n但係你又吹個垃圾政府唔脹 <br />\n永遠唔阻止蝗蟲入境 又等到事態嚴重先公布疫情<br />\n咁可以點做？<br />\n咪用返佢哋最鍾意嘅